-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\', 宋体, \'Myriad Pro\', Lato, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\n	REST是一种架构风格，Roy Thomas Fielding 2000年在加州大学欧文分校的博士论文 《Architectural Styles and the Design of Network-based Software Architectures》\n&lt;/p&gt;', '6', null, '2016-12-10 00:25:59', '2016-12-10 00:25:38', '2', '2', 'REST', '1', '2', '1', '1', '0', '0', '0');
